"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"assets may replace legal tender within 10 yearsã€‚\\n\\nAccording to the 2021 global blockchain survey report released by Deloitte, it is generally believed that digital assets such as cryptocurrency based on blockchain technology may replace legal tender in the next 5 to 10 years.\\n\\nIn a survey of 1280 executives and employees in different industries in 10 countries and regions around the world, up to 76% of the respondents expressed the above views.73% of respondents believe that their enterprises will miss opportunities or competitive advantages if they do not use blockchain technology and digital assets.\\n\\n81% of respondents believe that blockchain technology can be widely used, and 80% believe that the application of blockchain technology, digital assets and / or cryptocurrency can bring new revenue sources to their industry.\\n\\nRespondents pointed out that the potential application fields of digital assets in their enterprises include digital asset custody (45%), new payment channels or types (42%), investment / portfolio diversification (41%), asset certification (39%), etc.\",\"timestamp\":1637171697,\"title\":\"Blockchain technology has broad prospects: Russian media say that digital \"},\"digest\":\"TWv_XPdbiMgrft3dL-s0RnJ9Ya5_FU01ZGT9O2tOkrE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6C974C1a51427766f2253C34826a64C972C2bcc6\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DNenYCasEi4XyjHywVaq5_jvn6bleFvG7lmqXoeYo2o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ecvxSZxpf1GN88jLnv4JIxzi1Ry9xYGCoHxfMv64bbU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"yA1aWcGYR3WIWe9gH4KijTrjdZvP8el4izdXX7zxIIZxcFNy_p0i4o-a_su3ikeHBF_IpCglyo8lc96szKgfJw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb99fd4e48d61ab036953b8bc54601b051ac2bce858a1cd9026bd855745befb0d58f01ef6d58e4223369ad43aa5d68f2529441f67410758e9db20069a6e119ed01c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\